-- Russia VTB says paid off $3.1 bln syndicated loan this month
-- 
-- Fri Aug 01, 2014 02:01AM EDT
-- None



MOSCOW, Aug 1 (Reuters) - Russia's second largest bank, VTB <VTBR.MM> said on Friday it had paid off a $3.1 billion syndicated loan with its own funds earlier this month, before it was hit by Western sanctions.

